==Fellowship==
The RCN awards fellowships bestowed for exceptional contributions to nursing. Honorary Fellowships can be granted by RCN Council to those who are unable to become an RCN member, either because they are from overseas or because they work outside the nursing profession. Fellows and Honorary Fellows are entitled to the postnomial ''FRCN''.<ref>[http://www.rcn.org.uk/aboutus/gov/fellows RCN Award of Merit and RCN Fellowship]</ref>

